sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant B as Browser
  participant S as Server
  participant DB as MongoDB

  B->>S: POST /api/user-progress (seed, idempotent)
  B->>S: GET /api/ws/ticket
  B->>S: WS connect ?ticket&visiting_place_id
  loop every GPS fix
    B->>S: { type: "location", lat, long }
    S->>DB: place threshold + next unvisited waypoint
    S-->>B: { type: "progress", distance, bearing,<br/>thresholdMeters, arrived }
  end
  Note over B: arrived = true -> confirmation prompt
  B->>S: { type: "confirm_visit", route_id }
  S->>S: re-validate last position vs radius
  S->>DB: mark visited · award points (idempotent)<br/>log milestone · bump visitor_count
  S-->>B: { type: "visit_result", confirmed }
  S-->>B: { type: "progress", ... next waypoint }
